ac joints and can cause pain and stiffness, especially in the lower back and buttocks.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.022829,0.04286,0.062648,0.077167,0.097084,0.10801,0.11352,0.11923,0.11534,0.098111,0.077151,0.066048],"unified_progress":[0.025347,0.052101,0.077829,0.093866,0.10005,0.11871,0.11113,0.10649,0.099344,0.0922,0.070821,0.05211]},{"section":11,"text":"The eye inflammation and constricted pupil are concerning.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.045502,0.070771,0.076087,0.083213,0.085463,0.089437,0.093745,0.093218,0.091855,0.090072,0.089782,0.090855],"unified_progress":[0.050252,0.073058,0.078595,0.08411,0.089347,0.092138,0.090629,0.094267,0.092705,0.087041,0.085277,0.082579]},{"section":12,"text":"Ankylosing spondylitis can sometimes involve the eyes, leading to conditions like iritis or uveitis.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027976,0.047843,0.06729,0.080773,0.094385,0.10259,0.10744,0.11106,0.10839,0.09825,0.081384,0.072619],"unified_progress":[0.031603,0.057521,0.082614,0.091484,0.097442,0.11025,0.10494,0.10217,0.097873,0.090936,0.074962,0.0582]},{"section":13,"text":"The pupil being constricted might indicate some involvement of the oculomotor nerve or inflammation around the eye, which is common in spondylitis.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.042189,0.047329,0.065608,0.079331,0.092949,0.10179,0.10741,0.10977,0.10646,0.095955,0.082148,0.069058],"unified_progress":[0.041449,0.058757,0.077444,0.090047,0.097366,0.10429,0.10381,0.10231,0.09876,0.091604,0.075633,0.058537]},{"section":14,"text":"The physical exam findings of paravertebral muscle tenderness and tenderness at the iliac crest and ischial tuberosity also align with ankylosing spondylitis, as it affects the surrounding muscles and bones in that area.","dimension":1,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.037596,0.051755,0.07054,0.084795,0.095171,0.1