liitis are a big clue.","dimension":10,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033229,0.067414,0.087672,0.098415,0.10138,0.10086,0.10135,0.096002,0.09099,0.084188,0.074892,0.063608],"unified_progress":[0.034175,0.066018,0.084309,0.096005,0.10239,0.10203,0.10161,0.098327,0.097462,0.088124,0.072855,0.056696]},{"section":12,"text":"Sacroiliitis refers to inflammation of the sacroiliac joint, which is a hallmark of ankylosing spondylitis, especially in the early stages.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034285,0.057316,0.074333,0.087149,0.097145,0.10132,0.10813,0.10635,0.099723,0.089762,0.077686,0.066794],"unified_progress":[0.031507,0.059946,0.081423,0.095619,0.10191,0.11336,0.10547,0.10058,0.097207,0.085668,0.070798,0.056517]},{"section":13,"text":"Ankylosing spondylitis is a type of inflammatory arthritis that primarily affects the spine and sacroiliac joints.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028532,0.049891,0.065991,0.078695,0.092831,0.10012,0.11186,0.114,0.10645,0.096801,0.083135,0.071691],"unified_progress":[0.027655,0.05434,0.07736,0.093713,0.099732,0.11764,0.10933,0.10422,0.097862,0.089645,0.071885,0.056623]},{"section":14,"text":"It often presents with chronic back pain, stiffness, and can involve other areas like the eyes, causing iritis or uveitis, which explains the eye inflammation and constricted pupil.","dimension":14,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.040067,0.061549,0.069926,0.075768,0.085538,0.090788,0.098582,0.10204,0.10136,0.092915,0.09364,0.087823],"unified_progress":[0.057213,0.08318,0.083873,0.086796,0.091286,0.096717,0.093979,0.095865,0.091469,0.085184,0.074199,0.060239]},{"section":15,"text":"The eye symptoms here are likely uveitis, which is common in ankylosing spondylitis.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031041,0.050208,0.065334,0.07585,0.086407,0.092663,0.1007,0.10451,0.10405,0.10178,0.096155,0.091305],"unifie